race.description: Aviso Tas Insurance Brokers Maiden Plate
race.comment: A QUEENS BUZZ (9) improved again when narrowly beaten over 1400m at Launceston. Grace takes over from the apprentice, and she jumps from the inside barrier. Ready to win. SAVAGE RIVER (5) draws wide but is busting to win and comes back from a mile with the blinkers on for the first time. Keeps Newitt and will be right in it if things go his way. Stablemate NANDI CLAN (12) is fourth up, and it wouldn't surprise to see more from her returning to a sprint. Each way claims. COLLEEN'S CROWN (6) will present at peak fitness and was cruelled by the 13 gate at Launceston last time. Draws inside today and has a key gear switch. Is on a quick back-up and keeps the handy 2kg claim.
